                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/10044" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CPGN-0298</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">611 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">ESG赋能国企治理，助力山西汾酒高质量发展</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">ESG enhances the governance of state-owned enterprises, supporting the high-quality development of Shanxi Fenjiu</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">邵帅，陈祥，葛力铭，杨莉莉</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">华东理工大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">山西杏花村汾酒集团有限责任公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">食品工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">党群部门/思想政治工作部门/企业文化部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">11 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">ESG；企业治理；山西汾酒；绿色低碳转型；高质量发展</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">ESG; Corporate governance; Shanxi Fenjiu; Green low-carbon transformation; High-quality development</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">ESG作为一种综合治理框架，助力企业在追求经济效益的同时平衡环境保护、社会责任与公司治理，以实现可持续发展目标。本案例为描述性案例，深入探讨了山西汾酒如何融入ESG理念，从而实现绿色低碳转型和高质量发展。案例表明，在“双碳”目标指引和董事长袁清茂的带领下，山西汾酒依托复兴“123”纲领和“八大纲领”等战略框架，构建了独特的ESG体系，从绿色原粮基地建设、低碳生产到社会责任履行，再到治理能力优化，逐步形成了完善的可持续发展路径。本案例展示了ESG在赋能山西汾酒过程中，如何推动财务表现和品牌价值提升，同时增强市场认可，为白酒行业的绿色转型提供了宝贵借鉴。通过本案例，学生能够深入理解ESG在企业治理中的核心作用，领悟其在推动可持续发展中的重要意义，并为未来企业如何实现高质量发展提供重要启示。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">ESG, as a comprehensive governance framework, enables companies to balance economic performance with environmental protection, social responsibility, and corporate governance, achieving sustainable development goals. This descriptive case study explores how Shanxi Fenjiu has integrated ESG principles to achieve green, low-carbon transformation and high-quality growth. The case demonstrates that, under the guidance of China’s carbon peaking and carbon neutrality goals and the leadership of Chairman Yuan Qingmao, Shanxi Fenjiu has leveraged strategic frameworks such as the 123 Revival Program and the Eight Principles to build a unique ESG system. Through initiatives ranging from the establishment of green raw material bases and low-carbon production processes to the fulfillment of social responsibilities and enhancement of governance capabilities, the company has gradually formed a comprehensive sustainable development pathway. This case illustrates how ESG has empowered Shanxi Fenjiu to drive financial performance and brand value, while also strengthening market recognition, providing valuable insights for the green transformation of the liquor industry. Through this case, students can gain a deeper understanding of the central role of ESG in corporate governance, appreciate its significance in fostering sustainable development, and offers valuable insights for guiding future enterprises in achieving high-quality development.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《公司治理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">可持续发展理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-11</td>
